title: Car models that will be discontinued for 2016
text:
More than a dozen cars will be discontinued for 2016, including the Dodge Caravan and Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution.
According to a list compiled by the Chicago Tribune , production for these cars will end due to several factors, including newer models have made it obsolete or sales were just not good enough to warrant more production. Whatever the reason, some of the most recognizable cars will not be seen on the road anymore.
Honda and Mini Cooper are stopping production for more than one car, with the former trying to focus more on their alternative fuel line.
